{"tid":2222152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學校全面恢復面授課堂　校長稱有學生退學返內地就學","createTime":"2020-09-29T02:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T03:28:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"372c7218dabf1d767262243da1d764acbca708c7","tid":2222152,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:02:42.000Z","msg":"全港學校繼上周三第一階段恢復面授課後，今日中二至中四、小二至小四、幼稚園低班及幼兒班學生，都可以返回校園。<br />\n<br />\n其中在上水鳳溪第一小學，有跨境學生提早到香港隔離14日，準備今日回校上課。四年級的吳同學表示，現時居於將軍澳，與爸爸及祖母同住，媽媽留在深圳。她表示，可以回校上課感到開心，因為已7個月沒有見到老師及同學，在深圳期間只能打電話與同學溝通。三年級的楊同學表示，現時居於祖母家，在深圳期間感到無聊，很想回港上課。<br />\n<br />\n校長朱偉林表示，全校有約一半屬跨境生，現時有約20名學生提早回港隔離，部分學生需要隔離至下月才能回校。他又表示，早前有14名學生退學，選擇回內地讀書。<br />\n<br />\n朱偉林提到，會將接受面授課程的學生集中在一個班別，安排面授課程的學生在另一班別，兩批學生的時間表一樣，每20分鐘課堂都會有5分鐘休息時間。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552178-20200929.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552178-20200929.htm&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXP2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=04d4ae8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552178-20200929.htm&h=46508add\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552178-20200929.htm</a>"},{"pid":"424abe80491b10af15c053bcc252ab5348743e06","tid":2222152,"uid":37487,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:04:01.000Z","msg":"支那仔快d躝"},{"pid":"c2fd5c262868584c986c7c895c128d99641aee40","tid":2222152,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:05:16.000Z","msg":"上水鳳溪第一小學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間超多跨境學生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b4943dffe8f0fecf65c8880770f2344ef9f5a4","tid":2222152,"uid":249094,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:06:31.000Z","msg":"好行唔送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後咪撚嚟<br />\n祝你肺炎死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded28c35a373f00ad21ee477cfde7d527637d6a4","tid":2222152,"uid":212454,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:09:45.000Z","msg":"早前有14名學生退學，選擇回內地讀書&lt;&lt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4b7ea07c81fd91268bf5061874322ff4be6547","tid":2222152,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:13:46.000Z","msg":"跨區返學,就好似大馬人去新加坡返學咁on9"},{"pid":"95891a5f030ae6fa7f261d8ae3978405a762b594","tid":2222152,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:17:16.000Z","msg":"深圳大把好學校 點解唔去讀?<br />\n走黎香港牛屎地方讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460e9f74689a733b2063122de1732ac4f067d27a","tid":2222152,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"95891a5f030ae6fa7f261d8ae3978405a762b594","tid":2222152,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:17:16.000Z","msg":"深圳大把好學校 點解唔去讀?<br />\n走黎香港牛屎地方讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:17:22.000Z","msg":"支那人材濟濟，高校林立，山川壯麗，物產豐隆，東亞稱雄，點解要來香港鳥語教學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce8c5dee46f1d0961fd99f4ddf9e6de2db7c1eb","tid":2222152,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" cla